{"tid":944848,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[沙中線]陳帆:事件涉私人公司爭拗,局方不會給予太多關注","createTime":"2018-12-17T12:17:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-19T13:19:34.000Z","uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"75bee8a31b257019e721754fb5adb48af80d92fa","tid":944848,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T12:17:46.000Z","msg":"沙中綫紅磡站擴建工程調查委員會繼續召開聆訊，運輸及房屋局局長陳帆已完成作供。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">總承建商禮頓的代表律師指，分判商中科興業董事潘焯鴻去年9月發電郵予運房局，要求沙中綫各單位會面的電郵，關注陳帆事後認為是否有需要與潘焯鴻會面。陳帆指，在今年傳媒報道事件後，政府及港鐵亦有調查，政府目前已全盤掌握工程涉及的問題，是否需要與潘焯鴻會面有不同的考慮。<br />\n<br />\n他說，局方去年收到電郵後，已按既定程序處理，潘焯鴻當時亦回覆指已完滿解決，現時重看電郵，認為事件可能涉及私人公司之間的爭拗，局方不會給予太多關注。</span><br />\n<br />\n陳帆回應潘焯鴻聲稱工程有大量鋼筋被剪時指，政府認為最適當做法是交予警方跟進，因為事件涉及刑事成份。但禮頓的律師質疑，政府與警方的調查焦點並不一樣，陳帆表示不同意，認為焦點一樣是公眾安全。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1433669-20181217.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1433669-20181217.htm&d=4fxo2yBMJBQe44kZOiiPxNZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=b3f4b3ea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1433669-20181217.htm&h=b1fa253a\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1433669-20181217.htm</a>"},{"pid":"d0389ff1bb14509725f33a6a1225a132d026708c","tid":944848,"uid":149494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T12:20:16.000Z","msg":"即係舊年政府輕視個問題<br />\n到今年比傳媒踢爆單野先開始做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n局長喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 30萬1個月喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"078b691686620e144288469e10cea2a9591a871b","tid":944848,"uid":171192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T13:19:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_b.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_g.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_p.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_y.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}